msgstr "ເລືອກຕົວເລືອກນີ້ເພື່ອເປີດ Thunar ໃໝ່ໃນຮູບແບບແທັບພາຍໃຕ້ໜ້າຕ່າງ Thunar ທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ"

#: thunar/thunar-preferences-dialog.c:1141
msgid "Show full directory paths in tab titles"
msgstr "ສະແດງເສັ້ນທາງໄດເຣັກທໍຣີເຕັມໃນຊື່ແທັບ"

#: thunar/thunar-preferences-dialog.c:1147
msgid ""
"Select this option to show the full directory path in the tab title instead "
